SELECT Doctors.doctor_name, COUNT(Appointments.appointment_id) AS appointment_count FROM Doctors LEFT JOIN Appointments ON Doctors.doctor_id = Appointments.doctor_id GROUP BY Doctors.doctor_name ORDER BY appointment_count DESC;
